		<div id="content"><div class="how-it-works wm">
	<h3>How it works</h3>
	<p>Sur.ly replaces any user-posted outbound links which safety is <br> not yet approved with its indirect safe links to the same target pages.</p>
	<div style="padding:60px 0 30px 0;"><img src="surly/images/design/hiw-001.png" alt="" /></div>

