<div class="toolbar-informs wm">
	<h3>Sur.ly toolbar informs and retains visitors</h3>
	<p>When users follow an outbound link replaced by Sur.ly they see its toolbar at the top of the target page. <br />Sur.ly toolbar helps users to keep an eye on your site while they are browsing any external sources <br />linked to it. This toolbar is customizable and includes a set of options to retain your visitors.</p>
